en_684332_0	68 Division troops of the Security Force Headquarters - Mullaittivu (SFHQ-MLT) with the consent of all serving troops have volunteered to supply three major meals on every Saturday to the Iniya Walwu Illam Child Care Centre (Children’s Home) in Puthukkudiyiruppu with the hope of promoting goodwill and reconciliation.
en_684332_1	The project has been continuing for some time, considering the humanitarian aspect.
en_684332_2	Major General H.R.N Fernando, General Officer Commanding (GOC), 68 Division is closely supervising the charity programme after he was appointed the GOC.
en_684332_3	The inmates in the children’s home include 19 mentally-retarded kids.
